[[Classes]]: {{Class}} &rarr; {{Class|AmbientSound}} &rarr; <u>AmbientSoundNoGravity</u><br>

This thing is used like the {{Class|AmbientSound}} thing in the [[UDMF]] or Hexen [[map format]], but in addition is not affected by gravity and can therefore be placed at specific heights. It plays an ambient sound determined by its first parameter. The sounds themselves must be defined in [[SNDINFO]]. While some ambient sounds are defined in [[Predefined sounds|ZDoom.pk3]], none of them are actually added to the index of ambient sounds with the $ambient command, so a map using this thing needs a SNDINFO lump. 

==== [[DECORATE]] definition ====
 ACTOR <u>AmbientSoundNoGravity</u> : {{Class|AmbientSound}}
 {
   +{{Flag|NOGRAVITY}}
 }

